revision.text: '''Where:''' *name should be filled with the name of the dungeon. *image should be filled with the background image of the dungeon (from the screen before you start the dungeon). *caption should be filled with a description of the image spot. *tokens should be filled with the number of dungeon tokens needed to enter the dungeon. *location should be filled with the general location of the dungeon; i.e., Viridian Forest is north of Viridian City on Route 2.
revision.comment: Importing a new version from external source
